T1 37 Anonymous4 : A common work around for that problem is to initiate a plot sequence at the beginning of a scene change.
T1 38 Anonymous4 : This method is more common for large world and 3rd person.
T1 39 Anonymous4 : Another approach is a penalty system where the player is punished for destroying a plot sequence.
T1 40 Anonymous4 : This method is used frequently in first person shooters where a mission is failed due to friendly fire.
