T9 334 Anonymous25 : You can't even drive a real car very well through a remote joystick, let alone a game pad.
T9 335 Anonymous25 : I've actually done that; using a remote steering wheel is a huge improvement over a joystick.
T9 336 Anonymous25 : In driving games for consoles, the physics is tweaked to make the car incredibly stable.
T9 337 Anonymous25 : Lowering the center of gravity to below ground is a common trick.
